It’s about how you build the vibe and story telling, which Jaehyun is doing super-duper good here and of course with his unique voice. Everything makes SMOKE soooo dreamy and Jaehyunie🤍 …   ..  . author: @Necroherz
text:
It felt like watching p0rn Jaehyun-aaaahhh!!! I was giggling, feeling seduced and on my knees the entire 25:50 minutes of recording behind the scenes video and THE VOCALS!!! My man has demonstrating once again that he's not just a pretty face. Jaehyun has a rich bass/low/baritone voice that can make you feel vibrating the whole time. The beautiful runs, the vibrato, the high notes full of his warm dark tone ufff the whole process was exquisite to liste and ON TOP OF THAT i need to point the fact that he needed to lower the lights, be in the dark, to get into the character, into the emotion that the song demands. You can really see that even to sing a song you need to immerse yourself in the vibe of the lyrics and the mood in which it must be delivered. Being an experienced actor was also such a huge help to make the final result genuine, honest and be able to engage with your audience with your fans... Jaehyun you never stop to amaze me and making me feel proud 🥺💚

Ps: The moans, groans, whimpers, the heavy breathing, the facial gestures, the eyes closed, the sexy low voice for the adlibs and harmonies... HELP I'm not your strongest soldier Jaehyun-ahh... 🫠
